{"tid":1754423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打賭何君堯落選 連登仔「找數」維園裸跑","createTime":"2019-11-25T07:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:59:29.000Z","uid":178875,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d242a8ee292be8acb98bdfaca62e5aa6511cb1bd","tid":1754423,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191125/_2019112511525941206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191125%2F_2019112511525941206.jpg&h=d4b2ea85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔「找數」維園裸跑。網上圖片<br />\n區議會選舉結束，民主派取得過半數議席，不少建制派議員在今次選舉中「落馬」。有網民昨打賭若屯門樂翠區的何君堯落選，就會在維園裸跑，今早網上流傳一張圖片，見到有人深夜在維園裸跑，引起討論。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民稱讚事主是「找數真漢子」，亦有網民指因相片太黑，未能清楚見到事主，「好似影大腳八，尼斯湖水怪咁」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/34u8mG0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34u8mG0&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=972d0999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34u8mG0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af50bfd459ffb8bc11019d07a1d8be57809d914c","tid":1754423,"uid":45120,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"「好似影大腳八，尼斯湖水怪咁」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcedf257d17f9f0b5349961010433edfc25b04f6","tid":1754423,"uid":31151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"「好似影大腳八，尼斯湖水怪咁」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14edd31bcf99b9af